NAME
       stn - C++ wrapper facades for Berkeley sockets

DESCRIPTION
       The stn package provides a library of lightweight C++ wrapper
       facades for Berkeley sockets, for single threaded applications.

HOME PAGE
       The latest version of stn is available on the Web from:

            URL:    http://stn/
            File:   index.html           # the stn page
            File:   stn1.1.README   # Description, from the tar file
            File:   stn1.1.lsm      # Description, LSM format
            File:   stn1.1.tar.gz   # the complete source
            File:   stn1.1.pdf      # Reference Manual

BUILDING stn
       Full instructions for building stn may be found in the BUILDING
       file included in this distribution.

